Q1.What is Python?What are the ways to install python in PC?
Ans: Python is a general-purpose interpreted, interactive, object-oriented, and high-level programming language.
It was  first developed by Guido Van Rossum in 1991.The Name was inspired from “Monty Python's Flying Circus”, a BBC comedy series from the 1970s by Van 
It is free and simple to learn.It involves less code when compared to other programming languages
Web Development,Game Development,Machine Learning and Artificial Intelligence,Data Science and Data Visualization,Desktop GUI are some of the applications python.
Ways to install python in pc:
to install anaconda: 1.visit https://www.anaconda.com/products/individual 
2.scroll to bottom of the page and download the compatible version to your PC. 
3.once downloaded continue with install procedure with defaults and after the installation we can use jupyter notebook,spyder etc,.
to install python:
1.Visit  https://www.python.org/downloads/
2.download and run the installer
-We can also use pycharm,visual studio code,sublime,python idle for running python code
Q2.What are code environments?types?
Ans:Code environment is tab or place where we can write a program,compile or run a program and also view the output  of the program.
Types of the code environment:
1.Text Editors:These can be customized according to our requirements.we can write a code in any language. eg:visual studio
Full IDEs:It is Integrated devolpment environment designed for a specific programming language. eg:pycharm and spyder for python ,Rstudio for R
Notebook Environments:These are great tools for learning a lanugage,supports visualisations of data eg:jupyter notebook 
